@node Making weapons and armor,  , Maintenance cost, Training men
@subsection Making weapons and armor

Weapons and armor are required for the training of some kinds of
fighters.  Archers require longbows, for instance, hvy. foot require
plate armor, etc.

Weapons and armor are made with the @code{make} command (@pxref{make}).
The Weaponsmithing [1106] subskill of Combat [1100] is required to make
weapons and armor.

@example
@group
num   item           material
---   ----           --------
 72   longbow        yew [68]
 73   plate armor    iron [79]
 74   longsword      iron [79]
 75   pike           wood [77]
 85   lt. crossbow   wood [77]
 40   hvy. crossbow  wood [77] & iron [79]
@end group
@end example

One unit of the input material may turned into one of the desired items
each day.  For example, @code{make} 72 2 would spend two days turning
two yew [68] into two longbows [72].

