soldier         |   5         5
ninja           |   5         5
pirate          |  10 (30)   10 (30)
pikeman         |   5        20 (*)
fanatic         |  10         5
lt. foot        |  30        30
hvy. foot       |  60        60
angel           |  25       100
cavalier        |  75 (25)   75 (25)
knight          |  90 (40)   90 (40)
