added to the castle.  To use this skill, a noble should be inside the
castle to be improved and have at least 1 worker.

Strengthening the walls of a castle requires [78] stone.  The
amount required is the current hit rating of the castle.  For
example, to improve a castle from a hit rating of 110 to 115
requires 110 stone.

The effort required is 5 times the current hit rating of the
