continuously for two weeks, a Priest may create a holy symbol
consecrated to the Priest's diety.  The holy symbol increases the faith
of the Priest who possesses it and is necessary for many prayers.  This
prayer must be used in a Temple.

A priest may create a holy symbol for another priest of the same
religion, and a priest who finds or captures an appropriate holy symbol
may use it.  Since this skill costs 1 NP to learn, and is needed only to
create a holy symbol, a noble might be wise to instead buy a holy symbol
