Devotional prayer is the cornerstone of every religion.  By use of
devotional prayer a Priest gains holy power (piety).  Pray raises the
current Piety of the praying Priest by two.

To pray, the Priest must be in a Temple dedicated to his Deity.

See also @ref{Hinder meditation [2838]} and @ref{Hinder meditation [3532]}.

