current aura level.  The magician must be alone to meditate, which means
that (1) he cannot be stacked with anyone, and (2) he cannot have any
men or beasts in his inventory (except for ninjas, angels, and golems).

Current aura level will rise by four points if the magician is
the sole occupant of a tower and two points otherwise.  If the magician
possesses an auraculum, he will gain an additional two points.

Meditate can only be used when the magician's current aura level is
below his maximum effective aura.

