the caster will be shown, unless they are shrouding their abilities.
If a mage is employing an ability shroud, the aura invested in USE 2804
must exceed the shroud's aura, or that mage's current aura level won't
be shown.

For instance, USE 2804 1 will show the current aura for mages that are
not shrouding their abilities.  USE 2804 3 will show the current aura
