Clouds the target's mind with disturbing images and incoherent thoughts.
The target, whether mage or priest, will have difficulty achieving the
proper mental state during his next attempt at meditation or devotional
prayer.

The next meditate spell issued by the target may fail.  The more aura
invested in 2838, the greater the chance the target mage will fail:

@display
@group
