Each undead accompanying the demon lord fights with attack-25,
defense-1.

The demon lord's service is secured with a bond which lasts five
months, unless renewed.  Demon lords should be banished or have
their bonds renewed before the five months expires, or they may
exercise their wrath on the summoner.

Note that bonds expire on the 30th day of the month, regardless of when
they were cast.  The remainder of the month in which the spell was cast
counts as the first month.  So a summoning on the 15th day of the first
month of the year will expire after the 30th day of the fifth month.

